text: The 29th Acrobatic Gymnastics European Championships was held in Holon, Israel from October 30 to November 3, 2019. The competition took place at the Holon Toto Hall. This was the first time that Israel has hosted an acrobatic gymnastics competition at an international level. ==Participating nations== * * * * * * * * * * * * * '''''' * (Juniors only) * * * * *
